services.searchableText: ato entry point for government dept... if you require information from the ato and are making an enquiry on behalf of a government department or agency, your request for assistance can be emailed to atogateway.gov.authis service is only available in response to official requests from government departments and agencies (federal state or territory) - requests that do not come from a \2018.gov.au` or \2018.govt.nz` email address will be automatically rejected.alternatively, you can call (02) 6216 8600 during business hours.this number is only available to government departments and agencies - for individual and business enquiries, refer to the numbers listed below - we cannot redirect your call or provide any individual or business assistance. you require from ato making enquiry behalf department entry point dept tax taxation medicare health centrelink welfare benefits
